{"tid":1651781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以外國勢力為主嘅遊行，有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T12:53:11.000Z","uid":129988,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fe4188f00b37df3d84733295f08558f379031c","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"其實好多外國人都關注我地，<br />\n亦都有人話搞多國同時遊行<br />\n既然係咁，咁點解唔喺香港搞一次先？<br />\n邀請多國籍人士參與，<br />\n又或者有其他地方passport嘅香港人參與<br />\n由佢地舉返自己旗！<br />\n一來，畫面好睇，進一步推動外國關注<br />\n二來，再落維尼面<br />\n三來，有外國人，經歷話我地知班狗唔會亂黎<br />\n大家覺得可唔可行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b0788dc1df8dbc63015103cbf4fd01856b7c8e","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"相信大家都明外國勢力係必不可少，<br />\n所以由我地起頭好冇？"},{"pid":"a5b77c75e84f2607795e1427149175d9d38dc257","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"出親去都見到鬼佬，我相信佢地都會企出黎"},{"pid":"a7056746fda8b004388761876180c272ec0fabcc","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"加上呢排nba同暴雪，我諗係時候！"},{"pid":"bc7ac3eab19e80672a1e37ac5e617a294434e346","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a881aec19d884f2bb171ab44ab394470959b8f5f","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"cbb55b1b1e1592ef8ea94fccaea53e0349b71874","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab496cb90a43a26c526add397dedaf10b233240","tid":1651781,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"召喚外國勢力！"},{"pid":"84ffc170d21c2389